activities:
Concur provides web based employee spend management services including travel booking, expense management, invoice payment and related services.  Concur will import the personal information from its customers for purposes of 
-	hosting of the platform;
-	provision of the expense related tools;
-	recording, monitoring, management and reporting on travel booking and expenses.

In addition, Concur will receive HR data from its European affiliates.  Concur will import the personal information from the employees of its affiliates for purposes of 
-	managing and coordinating employee benefits;
-	managing and coordinating payroll;
-	HR administration.
